channel.title: Is there ever any kind of documentation with server sources?
channel.description:
Hey guys, I've just started coding pservers and I come from a heavy application development background. I'm used to being able to reference APIs and documentation for huge projects like this...Is there really no source that has any shred of documentation so I can actually do some work on the source without searching for a needle in a haystack?
At the moment I'm trying to fix my logout buttons. Seems that there's logout functions in Player.java but the buttons in-game do nothing. I'm using a 667 source by a guy named Humid.
